{"ts":"2026-06-12T16:19:03.304Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-yffj"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Extension activation failure is invisible outside pm health --json: extension list shows ok, no stderr hint, commands partially registered"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Repro: scaffold an extension whose activate() calls registerItemFields without 'schema' in manifest capabilities, install it, then: (1) 'pm extension --install ./my-extension' -> ok:true with no warning; (2) 'pm extension list' -> warnings: [] and the extension looks healthy (installed:true, status ok in discovery); (3) normal commands print nothing on stderr; (4) registrations made BEFORE the throw still work (my-extension ping ran), so the extension is silently half-active. Only 'pm health' (status warn, opaque string extension_activate_failed:project:my-extension) and 'pm health --json' checks[name=extensions].details.activation.failed expose the excellent error+trace+hint payload (loader.ts:2458 area builds it). Suggestions: surface activation.failed (error + hint) in 'pm extension list' output and in the install command result when the just-installed extension fails to activate; optionally a one-line stderr warning on command runs. The diagnostic payload already exists — this is purely a surfacing/discoverability gap for SDK developers."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","dogfood-2026-06-12","extensions","sdk"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-06-12T16:19:03.304Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-12T16:19:03.304Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"06c6d3c35c8db66d340d8b02bccbe6a5220889acce3eea3dd62fa4cecf14a515","message":""}
